collection.name: PeopleInThePlaceTheyLove
collection.description:
#Yusuke Hanai is coming to the metaverse!

**“People In The Place They Love”** is a collection of 1,000 NFTs- specially designed, dressed in unique hand-drawn attributes.
This is the 1st out of 3 phases of Yusuke Hanai’s NFT project. NFT holders are able to gain membership access to the exclusive Yusuke Hanai collectors’ community with ever-growing benefits and offers.

Visit [YusukeHanai.fwenclub.com](https://YusukeHanai.fwenclub.com) for more details.
